<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.9">
<l>vētamum vēḷviyum viṇṇu mirucuṭarum</l>
<l>ātiyu māṉā ṉaruḷtanta vānamakku</l>
<l>pōtalarum puṉṉaicūḻ pullāṇi kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>ōtamum nāṉu muṟaṅkā tiruntēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Ah,] the way that the one, who became the primal cause, the Vedas,</l>
<l>The sacrifice, the heavens, and the two orbs, grants us grace!</l>
<l>I worship, hands [joined], in Pullāṇi, surrounded by laurel trees</l>
<l rend="indent">where buds blossom;</l>
<l>[Both] the [sea] waves and I are sleepless.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
